OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of Giardiasis
OL,4,Cand how can it be treated?
OL,6,FTwo children at a Liverpool primary
OL,7,Fschool dealing with a Giardiasis
OL,8,Foutbreak have died, health authorities
OL,9,Fhave confirmed.
OL,11,FParents were first told of the
OL,12,Foutbreak at Millstead Primary School
OL,13,Fin Liverpool in May. The school
OL,14,Fteaches children aged two to 11 years,
OL,15,Fwho have special educational needs.
OL,17,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,18,Fsaid the causes of the deaths of the
OL,19,Ftwo children have not been confirmed
OL,20,Fbut they are "unlikely to be due to
OL,21,FGiardia".
