OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of Giardiasis
OL,4,Cand how can it be treated?
OL,6,FPeople are most infectious from when
OL,7,Fsymptoms start until two days after
OL,8,Fthey have passed.
OL,10,FIt is recommended people stay off
OL,11,Fschool or work until symptoms have
OL,12,Fstopped for two days.
OL,14,FYou can have giardiasis and spread it
OL,15,Fto others without having any symptoms.
OL,17,FHow is it treated?
OL,19,FGiardiasis is treated with antibiotics.
