OL,3,CWhat are the symptoms of Giardiasis
OL,4,Cand how can it be treated?
OL,6,FThe NHS recommend people return to
OL,7,Ftheir GP if they have symptoms a week
OL,8,Fafter starting treatment.
OL,10,FThey might give you additional
OL,11,Fantibiotics or refer you to a
OL,12,Fspecialist for treatment.
OL,14,FSometimes the people you live with may
OL,15,Falso need to be tested and treated.
